---
// import background image of target state
import fishing from '../images/fishing-1600.webp'
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 md:py-32">
	<!-- Background image with overlay -->
	<div class="absolute inset-0">
		<img
			src={fishing.src}
			alt=""
			class="h-full w-full object-cover object-[40%_center] md:object-center"
		/>
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/80 via-black/70 to-black/80"></div>
	</div>

	<!-- Content overlay -->
	<div class="relative mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
		<div class="space-y-8 text-center">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">
				Your Business Should Give You More Freedom, Not Less
			</h2>

			<div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-100">
				<p>
					You want a successful business that runs smoothly without you having to do everything. But
					without enough new customers coming in, you're stuck doing all the work yourselfâ€”leading
					to stagnation and overwhelm.
				</p>

				<p>
					We understand how hard it is to grow when you don't have leads coming in. That's why we
					developed a proven system that brings you qualified leads automatically, so you can focus
					on what matters.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Simple 3-step process -->
			<div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 text-left md:grid-cols-3">
				<div class="rounded-lg bg-black/30 p-6 backdrop-blur">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">15-Min Discovery</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-gray-100">Quick call to understand your business and goals</p>
				</div>

				<div class="rounded-lg bg-black/30 p-6 backdrop-blur">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Research & Strategy</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-gray-100">Our 23-point process finds what sets you apart</p>
				</div>

				<div class="rounded-lg bg-black/30 p-6 backdrop-blur">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Build & Launch</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-gray-100">Your lead-generating website goes live</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-12">
				<button
					class="inline-flex items-center rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-indigo-400 px-4 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:from-indigo-600 hover:to-indigo-500 hover:shadow-xl"
				>
					Get Your Custom Growth Plan
				</button>

				<p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-200">
					Stop worrying about where new customers will come from. Start focusing on growing your
					business.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<div class="bg-gray-900 py-24"></div>

<section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 via-white to-gray-50 py-12 md:py-20">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6">
		<!-- Main Heading -->
		<h2 class="mb-12 text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Growing Your Business, Simplified</h2>

		<div class="space-y-8">
			<!-- Vision -->
			<div>
				<h3 class="mb-2 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-indigo-600">
					Your Vision
				</h3>
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-900">
					At Rapid Rank, we know that you want to be an entrepreneur with a successful business that
					runs smoothly without your constant attention.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Challenge -->
			<div>
				<h3 class="mb-2 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-indigo-600">
					The Challenge
				</h3>
				<div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600">
					<p>
						In order to do that, you need a steady flow of qualified leads. Finding new customers
						online is harder than it should be, which leaves you feeling stagnant and overwhelmed,
						stuck doing everything yourself.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Approach -->
			<div>
				<h3 class="mb-2 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-indigo-600">
					Our Approach
				</h3>
				<div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600">
					<p>
						We believe your business should give you more freedom, not less. We understand it's hard
						to grow when you don't have consistent leads coming in. That's why we've developed and
						proven a 23-point sales research process that's generating consistent leads for local
						businesses like yours every single day.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Process -->
			<div>
				<h3 class="mb-2 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-indigo-600">
					The Process
				</h3>
				<div class="rounded-lg bg-gray-50 p-6 sm:p-8">
					<p class="mb-6 text-gray-900">Here's exactly how we'll help you succeed:</p>
					<ul class="space-y-4">
						<li class="flex gap-4">
							<div
								class="flex h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-indigo-600 text-sm text-white"
							>
								1
							</div>
							<span class="text-gray-600"
								>Start with a focused 15-minute call to understand your unique business needs</span
							>
						</li>
						<li class="flex gap-4">
							<div
								class="flex h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-indigo-600 text-sm text-white"
							>
								2
							</div>
							<span class="text-gray-600"
								>Conduct thorough market research and review our findings in a strategy session</span
							>
						</li>
						<li class="flex gap-4">
							<div
								class="flex h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-indigo-600 text-sm text-white"
							>
								3
							</div>
							<span class="text-gray-600"
								>Build and launch your custom lead-generating website designed for your market</span
							>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- CTA & Transformation -->
			<div class="space-y-6">
				<div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 sm:p-8">
					<p class="mb-4 text-gray-600">
						Ready to transform your business? Let's create your custom growth plan to start bringing
						in those leads.
					</p>
					<button
						class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border border-transparent bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-indigo-400 px-4 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:from-indigo-600 hover:to-indigo-500 hover:shadow-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
					>
						Get Your Growth Plan
					</button>
				</div>

				<p class="text-gray-600">
					You can stop worrying about finding your next customer and instead focus on what you do
					best - running your business - while a steady stream of qualified leads flows in week
					after week.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
